Euro-17 Ministers Set Extra Meeting for Today, Juncker Says

-- B y   F r e d   P a l s
-- 
2011-10-22T08:21:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/euro-17-ministers-set-extra-meeting-for-today-juncker-says.html
Euro-area finance ministers set an
extra meeting for today to follow immediately after a gathering
of the 27 European Union ministers, Luxembourg’s Jean-Claude Juncker said today in Brussels. They are preparing for a summit
of government leaders tomorrow, with another round on Oct. 26,
to deliver a solution to the region’s debt crisis.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Fred Pals in Amsterdam at 
